cast.name: Georgia Van Cuylenburg Georgia Van Cuylenburg

introduction: Some first dates can be an awkward, nerve-wracking experience. The stakes are raised considerably when John Frazier takes the shy but beautiful Ann Daniels to dinner at a particular restaurant. As the evening unfolds, John realizes the secrets he has spent years protecting are threatened by his inquisitive date. Devastating truths about the pair are exposed and neither will be the same after the explosive conclusion.
